<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Contest</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/contest.css" />
        {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/about.css"/> --}}
    {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css"> --}}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/foot.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="images/png" href="./img/favicon.webp">
    <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main_div">
        {{>navbar}}

    
        <header>
            <h1>Women Empowerment Contest</h1>
        </header>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="winners">
                <img src="./img/win-1.jpg" alt="" height="300px" width="400px" />
                <img src="./img/win-2.jpg" alt="" height="300px" width="400px" />
                <img src="./img/win-3.png" alt="" height="300px" width="400px" />
            </div>

            <div class="about-contest">
                <h2>About the Contest</h2>
                <p>
                    This contest is open to all women who are passionate about empowering
                    themselves and others. Whether you're a student striving for academic
                    excellence, a dedicated professional making strides in your career, an
                    ambitious entrepreneur with innovative ideas, or a nurturing homemaker
                    managing the household with love and care, you're welcome to
                    participate and showcase your unique talents, experiences, and
                    perspectives.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The purpose of this contest is multifaceted. Firstly, it aims to
                    celebrate and recognize the diverse achievements of women across
                    various fields and walks of life. By highlighting the accomplishments
                    of women from different backgrounds, cultures, and professions, we
                    seek to inspire others and break down barriers that may hinder women's
                    progress and success.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Furthermore, this contest serves as a platform to foster
                    collaboration, mentorship, and support among women. Through meaningful
                    interactions and networking opportunities, participants can connect
                    with like-minded individuals, exchange valuable insights, and build a
                    strong community of empowered women.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Most importantly, this contest aspires to catalyze positive change in
                    our communities and society at large. By amplifying women's voices and
                    advocating for gender equality, we aim to create a more inclusive and
                    equitable world where every woman has the opportunity to thrive and
                    fulfill her potential.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="overview">
                <div class="quiz interest">
                    <div class="left"></div>
                    <div class="right"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="Learning interest"></div>
                <div class="entrepreneurship interest"></div>
                <div class="leadership interest"></div>
                <div class="artist interest"></div>
                <div class="community-service interest"></div>
                <div class="Health-wellness interest"></div>
            </div>


            {{#if p1}}
            <div class="form-section">
                <h2>Register for the Contest</h2>
                <form action="/registercontest" method="post">

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="phone" name="Phone" required />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="age">Age:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="age" name="Age" required />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="address">Address:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="address" name="Address" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="hear-about">Where did you hear about us:</label>
                        <div class="hear-about-options">
                            <select id="hear-about" name="Hearing">
                                <option value="social-media">From Social Media</option>
                                <option value="friend">From a Friend</option>
                                <option value="website">From Our Website</option>
                                <option value="event">From an Event</option>
                                <option value="other">Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="interest">Field of Interest:</label>
                        <select id="interest" name="Area">
                            <option value="quiz">Quiz Competition</option>
                            <option value="learning">Learning Workshop</option>
                            <option value="entrepreneurship">Entrepreneurship Challenge</option>
                            <option value="leadership">Leadership Development Program</option>
                            <option value="art">Artistic Expression Contest</option>
                            <option value="community">Community Service Project</option>
                            <option value="health">Health and Wellness Initiative</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="comment">Comment:</label>
                        <textarea id="comment" name="Comments"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="ccc">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if p1}}
            {{else}}
            <a href="/seecontest1"><button id="contestButton">Apply contest</button></a>
            {{!-- <button id="contestButton">Apply contest</button> --}}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        {{>footer}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>